Welcome to our preview release
This is a preview of Swift Playgrounds for the BBC micro:bit, thanks for trying it out.
 
As this is a preview release, we’re expecting there to be a few rough edges. This is released as part of our micro:bit Tester Programme. If you’re not already signed up to that programme, please sign up now.
 
Do let us know about bugs, issues or suggestions. Either:
  • tap here to file a new issue on GitHub

  • tap here to raise a support ticket
 
Setting up your micro:bit for use with the book
In this book, we use Bluetooth to communicate with the micro:bit, and you need to flash the right hex file to your device over USB before you start.
 
Please visit http://microbit.org/testing#swiftplaygrounds to get the right hex file and for instructions about USB programming of the micro:bit.
Welcome to Swift Playgrounds for the micro:bit
